<DOC><DOCNO> WSJ871009-0110 </DOCNO><HL> Who's News:Litton Industries Inc.</HL><DD> 10/09/87</DD><SO> WALL STREET JOURNAL (J)</SO><IN> LIT WNEWS </IN><DATELINE> LITTON INDUSTRIES INC.  </DATELINE><TEXT>   Thomas A. Michalski was named president of the company's Applied Technology division. Mr. Michalski, previously vice president, programs management, at the San Jose, Calif.-based division, succeeds Vincent J. Battaglia, who resigned. Applied Technology makes threat-warning systems for military aircraft. </TEXT></DOC>